  <h3>v2.4 (10th of September 2009)</h3>
  <p>server component:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Plugin improvements
      <ul>
        <li>Nmap Upload is now using the <a href="http://rubynmap.sourceforge.net/">Nmap::Parser</a> library.</li>
